title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“[Jessye] Norman was in high dungeon, according to the gossip.” [From The Boston Globe, 17 February 1992. Submitted by Thayer S. Warshaw, North Andover, Massachusetts.]
